Create Lecturer
POST /api/lecturers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "LecturerNo": "600300",
  "FirstName": "John",
  "LastName": "Smith"
}

Get All Lecturers
GET /api/lecturers

Get Lecturer by ID
GET /api/lecturers/101

Update Lecturer
PUT /api/lecturers/101
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "LecturerNo": "600300",
  "FirstName": "Jonathan",
  "LastName": "Smith"
}

Delete Lecturer
DELETE /api/lecturers/101